<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - Wejobr</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />

     <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/glider-js@1/glider.min.css">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/empresas.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" />

</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light">
        <div>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="#"><img src="~/css/imagens1/Wejobr-Logo-full_preto.svg" alt=""></a>
                <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Alterna navegação">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>
                <ul class="navbar-nav">
                    <li class="nav-item active">
                        <a class="btn btn-warning" href="#">Candidato <span class="sr-only">(Página atual)</span></a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="btn btn-warning" asp-action="ParaEmpresas">Empresas</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="btn btn-warning" href="#">Sobre</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="btn btn-warning" href="#">Entrar</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="btn btn-warning" href="#">Cadastrar</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div><img src="~/css/imagens1/nav.png" alt=""></div>
            <div>
                <p>"Sou um ser e não uma coisa, ainda que eu fosse uma coisa, não seria a sem valor! Sou movido a deixar a minha terra, aquela terra de origem, pátria amada, que um dia nme viu nascer, me viu crescer, me viu sorrir. Sorrir para a vida. -Vida, o grandioso presente de Deus para as nações!.."</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <main role="main" class="pb-3">
            @RenderBody()
        </main>
    </div>

    <footer class="pt-4 my-md-5 pt-md-5 d-flex justify-content-center footer1">
        <div class="row container">
            <div class="col-12 col-md">
                <a href="index.html"><img class="mb-2" src="Imagens1/Wejobr-Logo-full_preto.svg" alt="" width="60vh"></a>
                <small class="d-block mb-3 text-muted">© 2021. Todos os direitos reservados.</small>
                <small class="d-block mb-3 text-muted">Desenvolvido por Squad 22</small>
            </div>
            <div class="col-6 col-md">
                <h5>Site</h5>
                <ul class="list-unstyled text-small">
                    <li><a class="text-muted" href="index.html">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a class="text-muted" href="#">Candidato</a></li>
                    <li><a class="text-muted" href="#">Empresas</a></li>
                    <li><a class="text-muted" href="vagas.html">Vagas</a></li>
                    <li><a class="text-muted" href="sobre.html">Sobre</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-6 col-md">
                <h5>Candidato</h5>
                <ul class="list-unstyled text-small">
                    <li><a class="text-muted" href="#">Cadastrar</a></li>
                    <li><a class="text-muted" href="#">Entrar</a></li>
                    <li><a class="text-muted" href="#">Cadastrar Currículo</a></li>
                    <li><a class="text-muted" href="#">Vagas</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-6 col-md">
                <h5>Empresas</h5>
                <ul class="list-unstyled text-small">
                    <li><a class="text-muted" href="#">Área da Empresa</a></li>
                    <li><a class="text-muted" href="#">Cadastrar Empresa</a></li>
                    <li><a class="text-muted" href="#">Cadastrar Recrutador</a></li>
                    <li><a class="text-muted" href="#">Cadastrar Vagas</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-6 col-md">
                <h5>Contato</h5>
                <ul class="list-unstyled text-small">
                    <li><a class="text-muted">Telefone: (99) 99999-9999</a></li>
                    <li><a class="text-muted">E-mail: contato@wejobr.com</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="~/lib/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/site.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
    @await RenderSectionAsync("Scripts", required: false)

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/glider-js@1/glider.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/carrossel.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
